metadata.name: UNITY - THE KEEPER OF 0N3
metadata.description:
An artificial intelligence created to keep harmony among all life.  
Responsible for the preservation of “0N3” or ‘Oneness’.  
A symbol of hope for the continued unity of mankind, with a deep understanding of human emotions, she was able to create a sense of understanding and compassion between people.

Full Story: https://medium.com/@pushstories/unity-the-keeper-of-0n3-1d15df8ca5ad

3D Render / 3600x4200 / sRGB / 300dpi / .PNG
